<div id="fb_body_wrapper">
<div id="fb_tab">
<div id="fb_tab_l">SetMouse</div>
<div id="fb_tab_r">&nbsp;<img src="images/fblogo_mini.gif" /></div> 
</div> 
<div id="fb_pg_wrapper">
<div id="fb_pg_body">
	G&egrave;re la position et la visibilit&eacute; du curseur de la souris<br \>
<br \>
<div class="fb_sect_title">Syntaxe</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><tt><br \>
<a href="KeyPgDeclare.html">Declare</a> <a href="KeyPgFunction.html">Function</a> <b>SetMouse</b> ( <a href="KeyPgByval.html">ByVal</a> <i>x</i> <a href="KeyPgAs.html">As</a> <a href="KeyPgInteger.html">Integer</a> = -1, <a href="KeyPgByval.html">ByVal</a> <i>y</i> <a href="KeyPgAs.html">As</a> <a href="KeyPgInteger.html">Integer</a> = -1, <a href="KeyPgByval.html">ByVal</a> <i>visibility</i> <a href="KeyPgAs.html">As</a> <a href="KeyPgInteger.html">Integer</a> = -1, <a href="KeyPgByval.html">ByVal</a> <i>clip</i> <a href="KeyPgAs.html">As</a> <a href="KeyPgInteger.html">Integer</a> = -1 ) <a href="KeyPgAs.html">As</a> <a href="KeyPgInteger.html">Integer</a><br \>
</tt><br \>
</div><div class="fb_sect_title">Usage</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><tt><br \>
<i>result</i> = <b>SetMouse</b>([ <i>x</i> ] [, [ <i>y</i> ] [, [ <i>visibility</i> ] [, [ <i>clip</i> ]]]])<br \>
</tt><br \>
</div><div class="fb_sect_title">Param&egrave;tres</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><br \>
(Pour chaque param&egrave;tre, <tt>-1</tt> est une valeur sp&eacute;ciale indiquant "pas de changements".)<br \>
<tt><i>x</i></tt><br \>
<div class="fb_indent">facultatif - coordonn&eacute;e x<br \>
</div><tt><i>y</i></tt><br \>
<div class="fb_indent">facultatif - coordonn&eacute;e y<br \>
</div><tt><i>visibility</i></tt><br \>
<div class="fb_indent">facultatif - visibilit&eacute;: <tt>1</tt> signifie visible, <tt>0</tt> signifie invisible<br \>
</div><tt><i>clip</i></tt><br \>
<div class="fb_indent">facultatif - limitation fen&ecirc;tre: <tt>1</tt> souris limit&eacute;e par rapport &agrave; la fen&ecirc;tre graphique, <tt>0</tt> signifie pas de limitation<br \>
<br \>
</div></div><div class="fb_sect_title">Valeur retourn&eacute;e</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><br \>
Z&eacute;ro (<tt>0</tt>) si succ&egrave;s, non-z&eacute;ro pour indiquer un &eacute;chec.<br \>
<br \>
</div><div class="fb_sect_title">Description</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><br \>
<tt><b>SetMouse</b></tt> validera les coordonn&eacute;es (<tt><i>x</i></tt>, <tt><i>y</i></tt>) du pointeur de la souris, ainsi que la visibilit&eacute; de celui-ci.  La position de la souris est valid&eacute;e en utilisant les param&egrave;tres <tt><i>x</i></tt> et <tt><i>y</i></tt>.  La souris sera visible si <tt><i>visibility</i></tt> est mise &agrave; <tt>1</tt>, et invisible si mise &agrave; <tt>0</tt>.  <tt><b>SetMouse</b></tt> est destin&eacute; aux modes graphiques initialis&eacute;s seulement avec <tt><a href="KeyPgScreengraphics.html">Screen (Graphics)</a></tt>.<br \>
<br \>
</div><div class="fb_sect_title">Exemple</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><br \>
<tt><div class="freebasic">
<span class="key">Dim</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">As</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">Integer</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">x</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">y</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">buttons</span><br />
<br />
<span class="com">'&nbsp;cree&nbsp;un&nbsp;ecran&nbsp;640*480</span><br />
<span class="key">ScreenRes</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">640</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">480</span><br />
<span class="key">Print</span>&nbsp;<span class="quo">"Click&nbsp;the&nbsp;mouse&nbsp;button&nbsp;to&nbsp;center&nbsp;the&nbsp;mouse"</span><br />
<br />
<span class="key">Do</span><br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="com">'&nbsp;recupere&nbsp;etat&nbsp;x,&nbsp;y&nbsp;et&nbsp;bouton&nbsp;(attend&nbsp;tant&nbsp;que&nbsp;souris&nbsp;est&nbsp;sur&nbsp;ecran)</span><br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="key">Do</span><span class="oth">:</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">Sleep</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">1</span><span class="oth">:</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">Loop</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">While</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">GetMouse</span><span class="oth">(</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">x</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">y</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">buttons</span><span class="oth">)</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">&lt;&gt;</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">0</span><br />
<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="key">If</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">buttons</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">And</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">1</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">Then</span><br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="com">'&nbsp;si&nbsp;clique&nbsp;bouton&nbsp;gauche,&nbsp;souris&nbsp;centre</span><br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="key">SetMouse</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">320</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">240</span><br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="key">End</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">If</span><br />
<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="com">'&nbsp;boucle&nbsp;jusqu'a&nbsp;Escape&nbsp;est&nbsp;appuy&eacute;</span><br />
<span class="key">Loop</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">Until</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">Inkey</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">=</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">Chr</span><span class="oth">(</span><span class="num">27</span><span class="oth">)</span><br />
</div></tt><br />
<br \>
<br \>
</div><div class="fb_sect_title">Diff&eacute;rences de dialectes</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><br \>
<ul><li> Non disponible en dialecte <i><a href="CompilerOptlang.html">-lang qb</a></i> sauf si r&eacute;f&eacute;renc&eacute; avec l'alias <tt><b>__Setmouset</b></tt>.<br \>
<br \>
</ul></div><div class="fb_sect_title">Diff&eacute;rences avec QB</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><br \>
